      {
        "children": [
          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 2,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": "Morbid",
            "type": "text",
            "version": 1
          },
          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": " has a beautiful world, a nicely teased story and responsively weighty combat that hooks you in with the bosses being the stickler that keeps you invested. However, it doesn’t offer anything standout over the game’s homages. Still, whilst it doesn’t offer much in the way of new value, it’s a nice alternative to slap on the Switch all the same with its hack and slash gutsy fun.",
            "type": "text",
            "version": 1
          }
        ],
